title: Catalan lawyers protest against arrest of Catalonia's leaders
text:
Catalan lawyers protest against arrest of Catalonia's leaders Monday, March 26, 2018 - 00:50 
Catalan lawyers protest outside Barcelona's City of Justice court against the arrest and imprisonment of Catalonia's leaders. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
